      <title>纽森宣布加州进入紧急状态应对野火</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/newsom-declares-state-of-emergency-for-california-wildfire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加州州长加文·纽瑟姆宣布进入紧急状态，应对野火，这场火灾迫使数千名居民撤离，因为酷热的热浪增加了全州发生火灾的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/newsom-declares-state-of-emergency-for-california-wildfire</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 16:28:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
