    <item>
      <title>众议院民主党人考虑要求拜登退出竞选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/biden-debate-disaster-will-cost-them-house-and-senate-democrats-fear</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名民主党高级官员表示，数十名民主党议员正考虑签署一封信，要求总统乔·拜登退出竞选，因为他们越来越担心拜登将让他们失去对国会的控制权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/biden-debate-disaster-will-cost-them-house-and-senate-democrats-fear</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 15:56:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据报道，拜登正考虑退出，面临越来越大的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/biden-faces-mounting-pressure-as-report-says-he-is-weighing-exit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，《纽约时报》刊登了一则爆炸性报道称，拜登向一位关键盟友承认，如果他在未来几天无法扭转公众舆论，他可能不得不放弃竞选连任，这进一步加剧了要求总统乔·拜登退出总统竞选的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/biden-faces-mounting-pressure-as-report-says-he-is-weighing-exit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 15:26:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>默多克的《太阳报》在英国大选前支持斯塔默的劳动节</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/murdoch-s-sun-endorses-starmer-s-labour-the-day-before-uk-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[鲁珀特·默多克的《太阳报》支持基尔·斯塔默及其反对党工党赢得英国大选，这是英国媒体界的戏剧性举动，反映出该国政局的瞬息万变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/murdoch-s-sun-endorses-starmer-s-labour-the-day-before-uk-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 14:28:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>勒庞竞争对手在阻止极右翼执政的斗争中遭遇挫败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/le-pen-s-far-right-faces-a-struggle-as-rivals-band-together</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙的中间派阵营和左翼联盟策略性地从法国立法选举第二轮中撤出数百名候选人，以降低玛丽娜·勒庞的极右翼国民联盟获得绝对多数的机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/le-pen-s-far-right-faces-a-struggle-as-rivals-band-together</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 13:35:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列在黎巴嫩南部击毙真主党高级指挥官</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/israel-kills-a-hezbollah-senior-commander-in-south-lebanon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列军队在黎巴嫩南部对真主党一名高级指挥官的车辆进行空袭，导致其死亡，这进一步加剧了原本已经愈演愈烈的敌对局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/israel-kills-a-hezbollah-senior-commander-in-south-lebanon</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 13:14:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊丽莎白·沃伦指责鲍威尔给予大银行首席执行官过多影响力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/senator-warren-accuses-powell-of-letting-big-banks-ceos-get-too-much-sway</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议员伊丽莎白·沃伦表示，美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔给予银行首席执行官太多机会来影响关键政策，包括高管薪酬和银行资本提案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/senator-warren-accuses-powell-of-letting-big-banks-ceos-get-too-much-sway</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 12:33:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国汽车城希望工党能启动电动汽车梦想</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/uk-s-motor-city-hopes-labour-can-jump-start-ev-battery-dream</link>
      <description><![CDATA[考文垂市宣布计划在英格兰西米德兰兹郡的小型机场建造一座巨型电动汽车电池工厂，迄今已过去三年多，这给人们带来了希望，即英国能够赶上在电池生产方面已经领先多年的竞争对手国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/uk-s-motor-city-hopes-labour-can-jump-start-ev-battery-dream</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 08:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
